- Yes. sire.

62
00:24:05.987 --> 00:24:10.616
Start cleaning this village
of these nefarious dead!

63
00:24:10.908 --> 00:24:12.410
Yes. sire.

64
00:24:13.536 --> 00:24:15.580
After speaking with our men.

65
00:24:15.830 --> 00:24:17.373
