69
00:24:30.428 --> 00:24:31.846
Yes. sire.

70
00:25:02.668 --> 00:25:06.005
Malacca. at last.

71
00:25:07.715 --> 00:25:09.759
This territorial conquest is.

72
00:25:11.219 --> 00:25:13.846
