76
00:25:27.568 --> 00:25:29.153
All hail King Manuel!

77
00:25:29.320 --> 00:25:32.615
Hail King Manuel! Hail King Manuel!

78
00:25:34.283 --> 00:25:37.787
As in Cochin. as in Goa.

79
00:25:40.122 --> 00:25:42.458
