89
00:26:16.951 --> 00:26:20.830
I can guarantee you
that I will conquer Aden.

90
00:26:23.582 --> 00:26:25.751
Once Aden has been conquered.

91
00:26:26.627 --> 00:26:28.254
I will build

92
00:26:29.422 --> 00:26:31.007
